events.name: 移動（ノルヴァーナの街）

parameters:
Rima: That's right. To lure Luna as they demanded, Wendy and I took
Mao and Mei to the forest and fed them to Sylvia and Hilda.

Rima: But you see, that was necessary prey to protect this town... no,
all the people of Jupiterino.

Rima: We can never beat Lucia and Sylvia. We're the resistance, but
we've been keeping a delicate distance by compromising with the royal
capital.

Rima: Rinny, you might not understand. It's unfortunate that you've
become aware of our relationship with the royal capital, but I want
you to understand.
Rinny: So, you're saying you all were 'fake resistance'.

Rima: Say whatever you want. We don't have powers like Luna's. It's
the wisdom we've learned to survive, to protect ourselves.

Rinny: It makes me sick. You sell out your comrades and then ask for
understanding? Never speak of Luna again with your filthy mouths.

Rima: If we had angered them, many people in this town would have been
killed.

Rima: We would sell out our comrades if it meant saving more lives.
Even if it was Luna, Mao, and Mei.

Rinny: When Mao and Mei were devoured by Hilda, all your tears and
your exhausted faces were just an act, huh?

Rinny: Then what? When Luna went pale with rage, vowing to avenge Mao
and Mei, you were pushing her into a fight she couldn't win while
pretending to stop her?

Rima: That's how we have been protecting... this town, the people of
Norvana.
Rinny: Don't mess with me, you piece of shit.

Rinny: I'm going to kill everyone in this town and all of you.
Hehehe...
Rima: Even the people of this town?

Rinny: I'll kill everyone, including your so-called protectees. This
town is a nuisance.

Rima: Rinny, you're a general of the Knights of Messiah, aren't you?
Ceres wouldn't allow such a thing, would they?

Rinny: That was Ceres' decision to make. I'm not a hero like Ceres and
the others.

Rinny: "Kill the unpleasant ones. Kill the ugly ones." That's all
there is to it.
Rinny: You all are ugly. Truly ugly.
Rinny: You and this town are a nuisance.
Rinny: Die for me to clear my mood. That's my motive.
Wendy: I apologize for deceiving you!
Wendy: We did something terrible to Luna, Mei, and Mao.

Wendy: But that was to protect this town... It couldn't be helped...
Ugh...
Rinny: A pitiful thing to do? It couldn't be helped?
Rinny: Hey, are those tears just an act? Like that time.
Wendy: Rinny... Ceres-sama would surely understand...
Rinny: I told you before, I'm not a hero.

Rinny: If Ceres were to betray a comrade, I'd cut down Ceres too. No
matter the reason.

Rinny: You all misunderstood me as a hero on your own. You and
everyone in this town are all going to die.
Rima: You...! How dare you do this to my sister!
Rima: Indeed, you are the "Cursed Child"!

Rima: Nothing has changed since the old days. You are the "Cursed
Child"!

Rima: But, Cursed Child, every member of the Norvanna Resistance is
skilled.

Rima: Even without Kyle, if all of us together face you alone, we can
definitely win! Lucia and Sylvia included!

Rinny: Fufufu... So the righteous Resistance is resorting to lynching,
huh.
Rinny: Finally showing your true colors. I'm delighted. Hero.
Rinny: Cursed Child, huh. I used to be called that, but not anymore.

Rinny: I am the Grim Reaper. The price for Luna, Mei, and Mao will be
paid with death.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Rinny, I'm counting on you to take care of everyone.
Rinny: Yeah. Leave it to me. Don't die.
Rinny: I can't forgive... I won't forgive...
Rinny: (Luna, I can't become like you...)

Rinny: (I understand their point of view. You would forgive them,
wouldn't you?)
Rinny: (But I... I just can't forgive them. Those who deceived you.)
Rinny: It's a blood festival!! Raaaaaaah...!!
Rima: Magus General Rinny!! You cursed child! Dieeeee!!
Rinny: What's wrong!? Come at me! Bring it on!!

Rinny: I am your Grim Reaper! I'll make sure all of you fall to hell!
It's a massacre!!
Rinny: (Luna, sorry but I can't keep our promise...)
Rinny: (I will become their Grim Reaper. I will never forgive...)
Rinny: I will execute every single one of you!
Rinny: Ugh... Gah... Haah... Haah... Haah...
